Class Rider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.youber.cmput301f16t15.youber.users.User
      • com.youber.cmput301f16t15.youber.users.Rider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Rider
extends User
    Created by Reem on 2016-10-13.

    Subclass of User and one of the two types of users that Youber has. A rider creates a request for a driver and confirms it. He will also pay the driver when the request is complete

    See Also:
    User, User.UserType, Serialized Form
